Kuwait denied reports that it will
serve as a mediator between the government and opposition in
Bahrain, the Bahrain News Agency  reported today , citing Kuwaiti
Ambassador Sheikh Azzam Mubarak Al-Sabah.  Kuwaiti newspaper Al-Seyassah said on March 27 that
officials from Bahrainâ€™s largest opposition party Al-Wefaq will
discuss a Kuwaiti initiative to mediate between the Bahraini
government and its opponents. Al-Wefaq said that day that it
